 	<li>Request needs to be made 4 weeks in advance</li>
 	<li>You are willing to make a donation of $500 to cover expenses</li>
 	<li>Mileage reimbursement for travel outside of Phoenix Metropolitan area</li>
 	<li>No out-of-town requests on week days</li>
</ul>
