[av_textblock size=\'\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\']
Liberty Wildlife accepts volunteers for duties such as daily care, orphan care, rescue and transport, hotline, fundraising, maintenance and administrative work. <a href=\"/volunteer/\">Click here</a> to learn more about volunteering.
