[av_heading tag=\'h3\' padding=\'0\' heading=\'Make a Donation\' color=\'\' style=\'blockquote modern-quote\' custom_font=\'\' size=\'\' subheading_active=\'\' subheading_size=\'15\' custom_class=\'\' admin_preview_bg=\'\'][/av_heading]

[av_textblock size=\'\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\']
You can help Liberty Wildlife in its mission. See the information on our Capital Campaign. You can also make a donation, become a supporting member, have your company become a corporate member, set up monthly withdrawals from your checking account, or name Liberty Wildlife as a beneficiary of your planned giving.

Liberty Wildlife, is a non-profit 501(c)(3) organization. Therefore, your donation is tax-deductible as provided by law.
