[av_heading tag=\'h3\' padding=\'0\' heading=\'Charity Charms\' color=\'\' style=\'blockquote modern-quote\' custom_font=\'\' size=\'\' subheading_active=\'\' subheading_size=\'15\' custom_class=\'\' admin_preview_bg=\'\'][/av_heading]

[av_textblock size=\'\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\']
Purchase a handsome sterling silver Charity Charm with the Liberty Wildlife logo, and the proceeds from the sale will be donated to further Liberty’s rehabilitation work. This program has been underwritten by Earth Friends. Charity Charms are available at Liberty Wildlife. 100% of your order proceeds will go to our organization.

