[av_textblock size=\'\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\']
Use <a href=\"http://www.goodsearch.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.goodsearch.com/</a> as your search engine, and put Liberty Wildlife in the area that asks “Who do you Goodsearch for?” Liberty Wildlife is paid .01 for each search that is done, and you can click to see how much has been raised so far.
