[av_heading tag=\'h3\' padding=\'0\' heading=\'Cleanup to Save Wildlife Meetup\' color=\'\' style=\'blockquote modern-quote\' custom_font=\'\' size=\'\' subheading_active=\'\' subheading_size=\'15\' custom_class=\'\' admin_preview_bg=\'\'][/av_heading]

[av_textblock size=\'\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\']
Liberty Wildlife sponsors a Meetup called “Cleanup To Save Wildlife” on the Meetup.com web site.

This is a chance for everyone in the community to help wild animals by picking up fishing litter at area parks – before it injures or kills a goose or duck. You can help by spending 30 to 45 minutes once or twice a month, while enjoying one of our beautiful area parks, and meeting great, like-minded people.

This is perfect for teachers, coaches, church groups and others that want to help us help wildlife. You can even schedule your own cleanup events at a park near you, and the community will join you to clean it up!
[/av_textblock]

[av_heading tag=\'h3\' padding=\'0\' heading=\'Environmentally conscious pest control\' color=\'\' style=\'blockquote modern-quote\' custom_font=\'\' size=\'\' subheading_active=\'\' subheading_size=\'15\' custom_class=\'\' admin_preview_bg=\'\'][/av_heading]

[av_textblock size=\'\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\']
Get information on <a href=\"http://callprobest.com/fundraising\" target=\"_blank\">environmentally conscious pest and termite control</a>.
[/av_textblock]

[av_heading tag=\'h3\' padding=\'0\' heading=\'Donate your used vehicle to Liberty Wildlife\' color=\'\' style=\'blockquote modern-quote\' custom_font=\'\' size=\'\' subheading_active=\'\' subheading_size=\'15\' custom_class=\'\' admin_preview_bg=\'\'][/av_heading]

[av_textblock size=\'\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\']
Wondering what to do with your used car or truck? <a href=\"http://www.vehiclesforcharity.org/Donate/LBW.html\" target=\"_blank\">Donating your old vehicle to Liberty Wildlife</a>, is convenient, easy, and may qualify you for a tax deduction.

All you need to do is to complete our simple online form or call 1-866-628-2277 and we’ll take care of the rest. We will pick up your vehicle, arrange to have your donation towed, and provide you with a tax-deductible receipt, all at no charge to you.
[/av_textblock]

