[av_heading tag=\'h1\' padding=\'0\' heading=\'This Week @ Liberty - April 10, 2017\' color=\'\' style=\'blockquote modern-quote\' custom_font=\'\' size=\'\' subheading_active=\'\' subheading_size=\'15\' custom_class=\'\' admin_preview_bg=\'\'][/av_heading]

[av_notification title=\'\' color=\'silver\' border=\'dashed\' custom_bg=\'#444444\' custom_font=\'#ffffff\' size=\'normal\' icon_select=\'yes\' icon=\'ue837\' font=\'entypo-fontello\' admin_preview_bg=\'\']
The intake total for the year is now up to <strong>1154</strong>.
[/av_notification]

[av_textblock size=\'\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\' admin_preview_bg=\'\']
OK, I\'ve been saying there is a new format for the blog coming for two weeks now, and here we are, the same old format, same old set up.  I wasn\'t pulling your leg, it really is going to change, but I found out the new blog can\'t go live until the rest of the web site is also up and running. So please be patient, one of these Mondays you\'ll see a new style and I think you\'ll like it!
In the meantime, let\'s take a look at the various happenings from the last 14 days of NUMEROUS intakes, tours of the facility, a killdeer family, and a lot of orphan great horned owls...
[/av_textblock]

[av_slideshow size=\'no scaling\' animation=\'slide\' autoplay=\'false\' interval=\'5\' control_layout=\'av-control-default\']
[av_slide slide_type=\'image\' id=\'728\' video=\'http://\' mobile_image=\'\' video_ratio=\'16:9\' title=\'\' link_apply=\'\' link=\'lightbox\' link_target=\'\']
Cayden the giver
[/av_slide]
[/av_slideshow]

